@jippie The F_CPU macro is correctly set to 1000000UL. As you say, the RF library is using that macro to set the attiny timer prescaler to the write value for 1MHz and 1200bps.
    #if F_CPU == 1000000UL
    TCCR1 = _BV(CTC1) | _BV(CS12); // 1/8 prescaler
    OCR1C = (64 >> speedFactor) - 1; 
